    "body": "Actually, I'm going to close this issue for now... on learning more about the issue, it turns out there's much less to account for here than I thought; ABI decoding will actually still mostly work in the bugged cases (it's not really an encoding bug as such).  There'll be something to do here if we ever implement Vyper \"full mode\", but I'm just going to close this now as the issue I originally though we should handle turns out to mostly not exist (and also to not be handleable on an ABI level).",
